Using the relation $h = 2\pi\hbar$, rewrite as

\begin{align}
	\mu(T,V,N) &= -kT\ln\qty[\frac{V}{N}\qty(\frac{4\pi^2 mkT}{2\pi h^2})^{3/2}] \\
